# S06-T03: Telemetry Inspector

## Objective
Raw telemetry data viewer with frame-by-frame inspection and field filtering.

## Acceptance Criteria
- Live JSON tree of last decoded frame.
- Field filter (search box).
- Hex view of raw `ArrayBuffer` payload (toggleable).
- Frame rate badge + decode error counter.

## Steps
1. Subscribe to telemetry bus (S04-T05).
2. Build JSON tree viewer (collapsed by default, depth=1).
3. Implement hex dump renderer.
4. Throttle UI updates to 5Hz.

## Invariants
- Inspector does not retain frame history (single latest).
- Hex view chunked (rows of 16 bytes).
- No editing — read-only.
